name: Feed Me (Jameda Locker)
description:
BIG THANKS To Dr. Erdreich and his awesome Youtube tutorials, which you can find here...

https://www.youtube.com/@MrErdreich

Another, big thanks to Soundly (all music and sound effects came from them!)

This game was made using the p5.js editor : https://editor.p5js.org/

I used the p5.play library created by  Paolo Pedercini : https://p5play.org/

As well as the p5.sound library created by Jason Sigal: https://p5js.org/reference/#/libraries/p5.sound

CONTROLS:

Use arrow keys to move left and right OR 'A' and 'D'

To jump use the space bar

The goal is to collect all the fruit before time runs out!

Do not run into those hunter beetles, they will eat you!

Click the screen to start playing!
